  <brief_title>Effectiveness of Dextrose Injection for Osgood-Schlatter Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 2 Study of Dextrose Injection for Sport-Limiting Osgood Schlatter Disease in Adolescents.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
